    "author_channel_id": "UC1wRkKYTJosVJgeg5vYDuBw",
    "text": "It strikes me it would be simpler and much more efficient to have 2 external cylinders, sitting over a double ended piston in the middle.\n\nLess friction, fewer places for it to fail and leak too.\n\nEssentially, an inverted tire pump.",
